title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 142-2.23 - Student
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 142-2.23 - Student

State Regulations
A
student
means an individual who is
enrolled in and regularly attends a course of instruction at a state-licensed
educational institution of learning leading to a degree, certificate or
diploma, or who is completing residence requirements for a
degree. Notes
